setType

public void setType(RequestType type)
             throws DimensionsRuntimeException
Set the product name and type name of the request to be created at once. The product name and type name are those associated with the RequestType object passed in.

Parameters:
type - an object representing a request type.
Throws:
java.lang.NullPointerException - if type is null or has a null product.
DimensionsRuntimeException - if type or its contained product throw an exception when accessed.

setDetailedDescriptionFileName

public void setDetailedDescriptionFileName(java.lang.String detailedDescriptionFileName)
Sets the file name that contains the detailed description for the request.

Only one of the methods setDetailedDescription or setDetailedDescriptionFileName should be used for one request. If both are set, the detailed description will be used, not the detailed description file name.

Parameters:
detailedDescriptionFileName - File Name of file containing the detailed description
